        <mxCell id="TmU2V9EiiaB76fZ9spht-24" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;color: #cccccc;background-color: #1f1f1f;font-family: Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace;font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 19px;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;/**&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;* Core booking flow:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;* 1. Validate the show is still accepting bookings&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;* 2. Acquire a pessimistic write lock on selected seats — prevents two&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;* &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;concurrent transactions from booking the same seat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;* 3. Verify each locked seat is still available for this show&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;* 4. Calculate gross total from per-seat prices (PREMIUM/VIP cost more)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;* 5. Stack all applicable discount strategies via OfferService&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;* 6. Persist booking + BookingSeat records atomically&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;* 7. Decrement show.availableSeatCount&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #6a9955;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;*/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
